{
  "name": "שליחת תלושים - Payslip Sender",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📑 Payslip Sender\n\n**Webhook URL:** `/webhook/send-payslip`\n\n**אימות:** Header Auth מובנה ב-Webhook node — n8n דוחה בקשות לא מורשות ב-403 לפני שמתחילה זרימה (ללא ניצול execution quota).\n\n**שדות שמגיעים ב-body:**\n- `email` (comma-separated recipients)\n- `subject`, `body`, `body_html` (RTL)\n- `send_at`, `send_at_utc`, `schedule_mode`\n- `scope`, `employee_number`, `name`, `department`, `category`, `month`, `count`\n\n**קובץ מצורף:** `$binary.data`\n\n### אחרי ייבוא:\n1. **צור Credential של Header Auth:**\n   - Credentials → Create New → Header Auth\n   - Name (header): `X-Webhook-Secret`\n   - Value: מפתח אקראי חזק (`openssl rand -hex 24`)\n2. **קשר אותו ל-Webhook node** (שדה Credential for Header Auth).\n3. הגדר Microsoft Outlook / Gmail credential ב-'Send a message'.\n4. Activate את ה-workflow.\n5. ב-HTML הזן: `שם-סביבה=אותו-מפתח` (למשל `orenmeshi=<secret>`).",
        "height": 460,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "sticky-1",
      "name": "הוראות",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [40, 60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "send-payslip",
        "authentication": "headerAuth",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {
          "rawBody": false
        }
      },
      "id": "1481da40-7567-497c-ad51-dbe6e5c3cbe8",
      "name": "Webhook1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [656, -656],
      "webhookId": "send-payslip"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const b = $input.first().json.body || $input.first().json;\nconst binary = $input.first().binary || {};\nconst binaryKey = Object.keys(binary)[0];\nconst file = binaryKey ? binary[binaryKey] : null;\n\nconst emails = String(b.email || '')\n  .split(/[,;]+/)\n  .map(e => e.trim())\n  .filter(e => /@/.test(e));\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    emails_array: emails,\n    recipients_count: emails.length,\n    subject: b.subject || 'תלוש שכר',\n    body: b.body || '',\n    body_html: b.body_html || ('<div dir=\"rtl\">' + (b.body || '') + '</div>'),\n    scope: b.scope || 'employee',\n    schedule_mode: b.schedule_mode || 'now',\n    send_at: b.send_at || 'now',\n    send_at_utc: b.send_at_utc || 'now',\n    employee_number: b.employee_number || '',\n    name: b.name || '',\n    department: b.department || '',\n    category: b.category || '',\n    month: b.month || '',\n    count: b.count || '',\n    filename: file ? file.fileName : 'attachment.pdf',\n  },\n  binary: binary\n}];"
      },
      "id": "9a4b99a2-bcb2-4fd5-8189-735a221b5531",
      "name": "Normalize",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
